dcterms:description: The Medical Information Mart for Intensive Care (MIMIC-III) is a longitudinal, single-center database containing data associated with 53,423 distinct ICU admissions for adult patients admitted to critical care units between 2001 and 2012.
dcterms:title: MIMIC-III

dcterms:description: The eICU Collaborative Research Database (eICU-CRD) contains data associated with 200,859 admissions collected from 335 ICUs across 208 hospitals in the US admitted between 2014 and 2015.
dcterms:title: eICU Collaborative Research Database (eICU-CRD)
